markdownContent:
“Thank you *so* much! This looks great, right? Seems to me that you have a good eye, I wouldn't have noticed half these things. I guess if you study history, you really do learn how to have a good look at objects.”

“By the way, I talked to Laura while you were doing your description, and she wants you to help Timea for a bit. Ah, sorry: she's the curator. You'll find her on the first floor in one of the historical rooms. Again, thanks so much for your help!”
